4 The universe is enormous, so the chances of us being the only living creatures are small. 4 Although we think we are intelligent and that we know a lot about Space, we have only explored a very small area. 4 We might be the only creatures that can travel in Space, but it is unlikely.
5 In fact, some people say that we might have been visited by aliens. 5 These people point to ‘wonders’ such as Stonehenge in Britain and the Nazca lines in Peru as proof that aliens have been here.
